Justice Priscilla Chigumba Chronicle Online Reporter New ZEC Commissioner Justice Priscilla Makanyara Chigumba has been sworn in by President Emmerson Mnangagwa at State House this morning. She takes over from Justice Rita Makarau who resigned from the post in December. Members of the Commission of Inquiry into the sale of state land around urban areas chaired by Justice Tendai Uchena also took their oaths of office at the same ceremony. More to followâ€¦